(9, 'login', 'login', 'page', NULL, '<p>If you have already registered, all you need to log-in is follow these few steps:</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Step 1:&nbsp;</strong>Click on \"Login\" button at the upper right corner of your screen.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Enter your Email and Password.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong><em>Forgot your password?</em></strong></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Don\'t worry, we\'ve got you covered. Just click on <strong>\"Forgot Password\"</strong>, provide us your Email address and we will send you a password reset link in your inbox.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 9, 0, 'Active', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-01-31 05:01:52', '2019-01-31 06:01:00'),
(10, 'register', 'register', 'page', NULL, '<p>New to Deals Drill? Register with us in few simple steps:&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Step 1: </strong>Click \"Login\" button at the upper right corner of your screen.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Step 2:</strong> Click \"Sign Up\"</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Step 3:</strong> Fill up the available form with all necessary details including your email adress, phone no., and etcetera.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Step 4:</strong> Click \"Register Now\".</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Log-in to your email account and <span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">follow the verification link we have e-mailed you to complete your registration</span>.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Welcome to Deals Drill!</strong></p>', 10, 0, 'Active', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2019-01-31 05:01:10', '2019-01-31 06:01:53'),
